\& #or
\& $md2_hex = md2_file_hex(*FILEHANDLE);
.Ve
.PP
\&\fB\s-1BEWARE:\s0\fR You have to make sure that the filehandle is in binary mode before you pass it as argument to the \fBaddfile()\fR method.
